where UI and U 2 are the velocities of the shell and the gun
relative to the moving platform. If the velocity of the
platform is V, then the velocities of the shell and the
gun relative to an observer who is at rest will be VI =
= U{ + V and V 2 = U 2 + V.
Substituting for U 1 and U 2 in our previous equation, we
obtain:
